      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FLY LIKE POTTER (7) finished in the minors last time when third (16.89) at Q Straight making it two minors from two runs. Has the ability and expected to go close. TOBIAS IVY (8) has performed well at his last couple of runs here, most recently when second beaten 1.5 lengths (22.90). Solid formlines coming through his last run. Will give a great sight again. FEDERAL ARLO (6) stuck on well last time to finish 2 lengths back in third (18.16) at Richmond Straight in a Maiden over 324m. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Bold showing expected. DAISY RAY (1) is a Bradley Belford-trained newcomer by Fernando Bale out of Manila Flash. Drawn well and should get her chance. Profiles nicely and can feature in the finish.",
